General.Name: Innlanz Ltd
General.Description: Innlanz Limited owns and trades a hotel in Hamilton, New Zealand. The company was formerly known as Mediland Pharm Limited and changed its name to Innlanz Limited in November 2021. Innlanz Limited was founded in 2002 and is based in Parramatta, Australia. Innlanz Limited operates as a subsidiary of Pacific Merchants Group Limited.
